csvPath <- '/workspace/adults.csv'

    header = FALSE, 
    skip = 1,
    sep = ",")
adults_df_rdd <- createDataFrame(sqlContext, df_local)
printSchema(adults_df_rdd)

registerTempTable(adults_df_rdd, 'adults_df_rdd')
